quran[6{c,v,t}:
12,64,"baap ne jawab diya"" kya mein uss ke maamla mein tum par waisa hi bharosa karoon jaissa iss se pehlay uss ke bhai ke maamla mein kar chuka hon? Allah hi behtar Muhafiz hai aur woh sab se barh kar reham frmane wala hai """
12,65,"phir jab unhon ne apna samaan khoola to dekha ke un ka maal bhi inhen wapas kar diya gaya hai yeh dekh kar woh pukaar utthay"" abba jaan, aur hamein kya chahiye, dekhieye yeh hamara maal bhi hamein wapas day diya gaya hai bas ab hum jayen ge aur apne ahal o Ayal ke liye rasad le ayen ge, apne bhai ki hifazat bhi karen ge aur aik bar-e- shutar (ount ka wazan) aur ziyada bhi le ayen ge, itnay ghalla ka izafah aasani ke sath ho jaye ga """
12,66,"un ke baap ne kaha"" mein is ko hargiz tumahray sath nah beju ga jab taq ke tum Allah ke naam se mujh ko Paiman nah day do ke isay mere pa seen zaroor wapas le kar aao ge ila yeh ke kahin tum ghair hi liye jao"" jab unhon ne is ko apne apne Paiman day diye to is ne kaha"" dekho, hamaray is qoul par Allah nigehbaan hai """
12,67,"phir is ne kaha"" mere bachcho, misar ke darul-saltanat mein aik darwazay se daakhil nah hona balkay mukhtalif darwazon se jana magar mein Allah ki Mushiyat se tum ko nahi bacha sakta, hukum uss ke siwa kisi ka bhi nahi chalta, isi par mein ne bharosa kya, aur jis ko bhi bharosa karna ho isi par kere """
12,68,aur waqea bhi yahi howa ke jab woh apne baap ki hadaayat ke mutabiq shehar mein ( mutafarraq darwazon se ) daakhil hue to is ki yeh ahteyati tadbeer Allah ki Mushiyat ke muqablay mein kuch bhi kaam nah aaski haan bas yaqoob ke dil mein jo aik khatak thi usay daur karne ke liye is ne apni si koshish kar li be shak woh hamari di hui taleem se sahib ilm tha magar aksar log maamla ki haqeeqat ko jantay nahi hain
12,69,"yeh log yousuf ke huzoor puhanche to is ne apne bhai ko apne paas allag bulaa liya aur usay bta diya ke"" mein tera wohi bhai hon ( jo khoya gaya tha ) ab to unn baton ka gham nah kar jo yeh log karte rahay hain """
